UID:YJFXRvsJEJbgmvF0wHA9t
SUMMARY:Demo Series: Intro to Paper Mache &amp\; Open Studio
DTSTAMP:20260409T031200Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260412T100000
DESCRIPTION:We’ll start the evening with a paper mache paste making demo\, 
	then demonstrate some of our applications for using it to make giant puppe
	ts. Demo guests are welcome to stay for the workshop and lend a helping ha
	nd to paper mache projects underway or make something of their own.\n\nhtt
	ps://fremontartscouncil.org/calendar/demo-intro-to-float-builds-open-studi
	o\n\nFrom Fremont Arts Council
URL:https://fremontartscouncil.org/calendar/demo-intro-to-float-builds-open
	-studio
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:all-events
CATEGORIES:Fremont Arts Council
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
